text: The 1926 Marquette Golden Avalanche football team was an American football team that represented Marquette University as an independent during the 1926 college football season. In its fifth season under head coach Frank Murray, the team compiled a 6–3 record. ==Schedule== ==References== Marquette Category:Marquette Golden Avalanche football seasons Marquette Golden Avalanche football
